# Marketing (`src/pages/site`)

- Shell: `MarketingShell` (skip for auth-only / system error pages)
- Primitives: `src/components/marketing/primitives.jsx` + `ProductPreview`
- Register: page file → `pages/site/index.js` barrel → import + route in `App.jsx`
- Nav: update `MarketingShell.jsx` when adding top-level sections
- Tokens: `--go-*`; match Product / Docs / Pricing density
- Auth marketing: `src/pages/site/auth/`
- System: `src/pages/site/system/`

Detail → `add-marketing-page` skill.
